(2284, 562, '_field_14', 'Hello,\n\nAfter Lontar closed, I\'m very glad and excited to see that another market for speculative southeast Asian stories is opening up. When you say that authors must come from the SEA region, do you mean geographically? I am 100% Vietnamese but live in the United States. Would you consider submissions from overseas southeast Asians?'),
