(2290, 564, '_field_13', 'dlshirey@gmail.com'),
(2291, 564, '_field_14', 'You’ve Made the Short List\n\nHello,\nOMBAK has been added to my list at dlshirey.com/the-short-list. There are now 800+ publications, like yours, that feature writers\' shorter works, not longer pieces. Click on over to see if I’ve gotten your info correct. It is categorized by maximum word count.\n\nPlease, if you think other writers will find this list valuable, I’d appreciate you spreading the word in a tweet or post. Oh, and If you know of other sites that I\'ve missed, give me a shout. \n—DL Shirey (on Twitter @dlshirey)'),
