(156, 1, '2018-07-18 01:13:53', '2018-07-17 18:13:53', '\n	SOUTHEAST ASIA\'S WEIRD FICTION JOURNAL\n			<img src=\"http://www.ombak.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/ombak4-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" />			\n				<p>Ombak is Southeast Asia\'s weird fiction journal, and we are seeking submissions for our debut issue. Bring your best, and we\'ll do the rest.</p>\n<img src=\"http://www.ombak.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/ombak4-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" />			\n			<img src=\"http://www.ombak.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/clarkAshton.jpg\" alt=\"\" />			\n				<p>Weird fiction is a multifaceted type of speculative fiction, focusing on the strange and bizarre. It includes unorthodox and atypical ideas, often explored in unconventional ways.</p>\n<img src=\"http://www.ombak.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/clarkAshton.jpg\" alt=\"\" />			\n				<a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"previous\" aria-role=\"button\"><svg version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\">\n<path d=\"M398.572,104.287L246.857,256.001l151.715,151.714c3.617,3.618,5.428,7.904,5.428,12.856c0,4.953-1.811,9.238-5.428,12.857 l-47.428,47.428c-3.619,3.619-7.904,5.428-12.857,5.428s-9.238-1.809-12.857-5.428l-212-212c-3.619-3.618-5.428-7.904-5.428-12.856 c0-4.953,1.81-9.238,5.428-12.857l212-212c3.619-3.618,7.904-5.428,12.857-5.428s9.238,1.81,12.857,5.428l47.428,47.429 C402.189,82.19,404,86.476,404,91.428c0,4.953-1.811,9.238-5.428,12.857V104.287z\"/>\n</svg>\n</a>\n				<a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"next\" aria-role=\"button\"><svg version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\">\n<path d=\"M113.428,407.713l151.715-151.714L113.428,104.285c-3.617-3.618-5.428-7.904-5.428-12.856c0-4.953,1.811-9.238,5.428-12.857 l47.428-47.428c3.619-3.619,7.904-5.428,12.857-5.428s9.238,1.809,12.857,5.428l212,212c3.619,3.618,5.429,7.904,5.429,12.856 c0,4.953-1.81,9.238-5.429,12.857l-212,212c-3.619,3.618-7.904,5.428-12.857,5.428